#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertypography.lua:611
msgid ""
"Would you like to respect or ignore embedded lang tags by default?\n"
"\n"
"Respecting them will use relevant typographic rules to render their content, "
"while ignoring them will always use the main language typography rules.\n"
"\n"
"The current default (★) is to respect them."
msgstr ""
"Vai Jūs vēlētos atzīt vai ignorēt iešūtās valodas birkas pēc noklusējuma?\n"
"\n"
"Ja tās tiks atzītas, tad tiks pielietoti atbilstoši tipogrāfijas likumi. Ja "
"netiks atzītas, tad galvenās valodas tipogrāfijas likumi tiks lietoti.\n"
"\n"
"Pēc noklusējuma (★) valodas birkas tiek atzītas."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertypography.lua:614
msgid ""
"Would you like to respect or ignore embedded lang tags by default?\n"
"\n"
"Respecting them will use relevant typographic rules to render their content, "
"while ignoring them will always use the main language typography rules\n"
"\n"
"The current default (★) is to ignore them."
msgstr ""
