#: plugins/coverbrowser.koplugin/bookinfomanager.lua:868
msgid ""
"This will extract metadata and cover images from books in the current "
"directory.\n"
"Once extraction has started, you can abort at any moment by tapping on the "
"screen.\n"
"\n"
"Cover images will be saved with the adequate size for the current display "
"mode.\n"
"If you later change display mode, they may need to be extracted again.\n"
"\n"
"This extraction may take time and use some battery power: you may wish to "
"keep your device plugged in."
msgstr ""
"Ekstraktēs metadatus un vāka attēlus no grāmatām, kuras atrodas esošajā "
"mapē.\n"
"Kad process sāksies, to var atcelt pieskaroties ekrānam.\n"
"\n"
"Vāka attēli tiks saglabāti ar adekvātu izmēru, balstoties uz esošo displeja "
"režīmu.\n"
"Ja displeja režīms tiks mainīts - process jāpalaiž vēlreiz.\n"
"\n"
"Ekstraktēšana nav ātra un ierīci vēlams atstāt pieslēgtu pie barošanas."

